WashObject_0:
(:action WashObject_0
        :parameters (?toolobject - object ?a - agent ?l - location ?o - object)

        :precondition (and 
		(objectType ?toolobject ScrubBrushType)
		(atLocation ?a ?l)
		(objectAtLocation ?o ?l)
		(cleanable ?o)
		(holds ?a ?toolobject)
		)
        :effect (and 
		(isClean ?o)
		)
)
